Virtual FTPD

This ftpd is generated in an attempt to simplify FTP server process.

Ftp configuration:

With no configuration file present this FTP server will:

Serve every user's home directory
Serve a shared directory (/ftp/pub)

Configurable:

Logging on a per user basis
Visibility of directories on a per user basis
Access to directories on a per user basis
Power user enabler.
Debug level
Log level
Bandwith limitation on a per user basis
